# Applications from Giovanni Pastori Piccirilli's Thesis named "New perspectives for the Bayesian Conditional Transformation Model"

This repository contains the codes for four applications presented in the thesis "New perspectives for the Bayesian Conditional Transformation Model".

## Repository Structure

The repository is organized as follows:

/App5.2       # Framingham heart study
/App5.3        # Sleep deprivation study
/App6.1        # Modeling the mortality rate from bronchial and lung cancer in Brazil
/App6.2        # Analysis of vehicle theft incident in the city of SÃ£o Paulo

Each folder contains source code, data, and scripts needed to reproduce the results presented in the thesis.

